{"tid":1782601,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"話你知點解唔夠過半都要盡力砌功能組別","createTime":"2019-12-14T06:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T06:31:01.000Z","uid":296165,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"58df80906eee0a2834fd7a40248d2bf3c7f81c9d","tid":1782601,"uid":296165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"好多人話功能組別贏唔到，唔洗選／你玩埋佢。。。但我想講：錯曬<br />\n五大訴求最終目標：雙真普選<br />\n制度內玩法就係選特首，再政改<br />\n第一步：選特首，有人兩日前立場新聞寫過，簡單d講，第二界別300票全掃、第三界別社會福利界60票全掃、第四界別區議會127票已經穩奪、立法會大約一半35票、攞埋勞工界60席選委係582票！！！只要飲食界、進出口、紡織、批發零售、宗教、體演文出攞到19票，特首就係我地選！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8F%9B%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E5%9B%9B%E8%90%AC%E7%B4%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%B0%E8%A1%80-%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2/?fbclid=IwAR2OqRJoS8zRMObYElS-uJ8P9rVleSqAqCImjY7okoJvhuNNVZJ_MLQW3D4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258F%259B%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25AA%25E9%259C%2580%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25A1%2580-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%25AD%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2OqRJoS8zRMObYElS-uJ8P9rVleSqAqCImjY7okoJvhuNNVZJ_MLQW3D4&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=332e584c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258F%259B%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25AA%25E9%259C%2580%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25A1%2580-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%25AD%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2OqRJoS8zRMObYElS-uJ8P9rVleSqAqCImjY7okoJvhuNNVZJ_MLQW3D4&h=c688ae57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8F%9B%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E5%9B%9B%E8%90%AC%E7%B4%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%B0%E8%A1%80-%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2/?fbclid=IwAR2OqRJoS8zRMObYElS-uJ8P9rVleSqAqCImjY7okoJvhuNNVZJ_MLQW3D4</a><br />\n第二步：政改。唔係選完個特首就贏。今次我地搶到盡每一席、犧牲左咁多人先選到，如果政改俾對家否決，下次就會輸！但政改呢，係政府提出嘅議案，唔洗分組點票，只需要全體過半。所以立法會每一席都要爭！！！<br />\n總結：宜家個重點係：<br />\n1. 狂組工會，反攻勞工界60席選委<br />\n2. 叫曬你識嘅中醫、工程師登記功能組別，第二界別只輸依兩組<br />\n3. 飲食界、進出口、紡織、批發零售、宗教、體演文出<br />\n4. 立法會全票過半<br />\n唔好再問點解要搶功能組別！<br />\n煲底見！"},{"pid":"d801cca2715e586adfdbf9c0d8dfb33b1394d598","tid":1782601,"uid":296165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"480eddeada435c476be6568b6be74406a08ad4da","tid":1782601,"uid":296165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"3913f8abf6f0e6016b012e7ad4cec25a2f54e3cc","tid":1782601,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"213238468ce616b3f8ce1a83999ed18e3940056f","tid":1782601,"uid":296165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3d9854b0296c9054400c3a23ad1fb3c673a9c67","tid":1782601,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"邊個話唔夠過半<br />\n<br />\n蕭生分析左<br />\n<br />\n有機會贏 <br />\n<br />\n不過冇人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢70歲人都盡晒力"},{"pid":"f3c810c8fee47b550aa475b014aa89509d8ab31b","tid":1782601,"uid":296165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"581dce593af8ebfb3bb11225ec26382f4a3d442e","tid":1782601,"uid":47110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a5468fc08fe26e32a5895f08c8f4e0f8618eaf1","tid":1782601,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse